| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4957 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e482c7b2-5c73-5c38-952c-44bbc2e67e5d"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
